ffers to pay for Drug addict’s serialization so they don’t have any more drug addicted babies. She either has them get their tubes tied or go on Norplant or another type of long term birth control. She also gives them money when it is completed.<br>
<br>
Her critics believe she isn’t really helping because she isn’t offering any way for these women to get help for their addiction. So she isn’t fixing the problem.<br>
