<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>&quot;We don’t allow dogs to breed &quot; Harris, 51 has said. &quot;We spay them. We neuter them. We try to keep them from having unwanted puppies, and these women are literally having litters of children&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
